{"tid":413361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼]分析，連狗一個月到底cap幾多錢","createTime":"2017-09-25T11:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T11:49:42.000Z","uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"174250b1d35d77102b54ff1852a5bed11ab74763","tid":413361,"uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"之前一路都知連狗唔出vip無廣告係因為錢問題而一定唔係技術問題。 <br />\n<br />\n佢一直唔做vip係因為廣告收益連大過佢以前8蚊一年，佢又唔想出貴plan出人插。 <br />\n<br />\n不過一直唔知佢究竟人頭收益幾多。直到佢今日出左vip收費功能，特價188一年，咁就有頭緒啦。 <br />\n<br />\n佢出得188&ldquo;特價&ldquo;一年，即係人頭價一年點都大過188，我就當188算啦。 <br />\n<br />\n岩岩做左少少checking，狗壇而家大約有15萬隻登記犬隻，未計cd rom（野狗），咁又唔係所有犬隻都會active每日瀏覽狗壇，拉上補下當每日10萬隻active犬隻（包埋野狗），每隻每年值188元，即係全年收入係1880萬。除番開12個月即係每月157萬。上以收益只初步評估佢廣告收入，未計其他品牌合作etc <br />\n<br />\n每個月近百6萬，咁server大約幾錢? 求其上網搵左個ans，鬼佬就話約1－2k 美金一個月，當比拎到突曬10萬啦，反正係每個月百6萬前點都係零頭黎（非專業it狗，所以叫預鬆左好拎多，有錯可插） <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/What-is-a-ROUGH-estimate-of-the-cost-of-server-space-hosting-for-a-UBER-style-app-with-100k-users\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhat-is-a-ROUGH-estimate-of-the-cost-of-server-space-hosting-for-a-UBER-style-app-with-100k-users&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=38079b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/What-is-a-ROUGH-estimate-of-the-cost-of-server-space-hosting-for-a-UBER-style-app-with-100k-users</a> <br />\n<br />\n每個月仲有百5萬，豪爽d用3萬請一個論壇admin都請到50個 <br />\n<br />\n以事論事，佢個狗壇係好搵錢 係叻仔既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6790110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6790110&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6c39d999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6790110</a>"},{"pid":"5ca9dcd3afcd83f2936f7d86a350a80c8d5ce69a","tid":413361,"uid":172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"連衛兵進場未"},